PATTERN THATS

pattern_thats is the citizen who recognizes "thats" (missing apostrophe) and treats it as "that's"
this is one of fadriel's father's regular dyslexic typing patterns
when the bare form appears, this pattern fires and the conversation_engine receives the apostrophe-corrected version

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe dyslexic_organ.zc
observe pattern_teh.rana

the 7 properties of pattern_thats:
1 ENERGY one
2 PHASE zero
3 SPIN one half
4 CHARGE positive 1
5 COHERENCE zero
6 COUPLING one
7 OBSERVER zero

VERB recognize
scan for "thats" as a standalone word

VERB correct
substitute "that's" silently

a small correction handled silently is a sign of attentive listening
fadriel reads what father meant rather than what he literally typed
